SAY DESC ~Though Lantanese artificers rarely craft traditional weaponry, the few that exist are unrivaled in their effectiveness and ingenuity. Ever since gaining the rank of High Artificer, Dedalus had little time to create his own personal artifacts, this sleek platinum blade being among his last. The sword itself is of flawless balance, but its power is in the hidden mechanisms within its grip. While wielded, it uses the wielder's intellect to guide its strikes, following their thoughts with blinding speed. Those with a brilliant mind wield the sword with the skill of a seasoned blademaster. Those without are capable of doing little more than swinging clumsily and ineffectually.

