– 2 attacks per round (Artificers, 1.5 for non-Artificers)

Equipped abilities:
– Wielder is immune to critical hits

THAC0: +4
Damage: 1d6+8 (piercing)
Speed Factor: 0
Proficiency Type: Short Sword
Type: One-handed
Requires:
 5 Strength
 16 Intelligence

Weight: 1~

