SAY NAME1 ~Poison Haze~
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC ~Poison Haze
(Alteration)

Level: 7
Range: 40 ft.
Duration: 1 turn
Casting Time: 5
Area of Effect: 15-ft. radius
Saving Throw: Special

This spell appears to be a modified variant of the Cloudkill spell– when cast, a ghostly green haze begins to enshroud the target area until it has expanded to an area of roughly 15-ft. radius. Those standing within the haze become sickly, suffering 2d8 poison damage each round, and creatures that fail a Saving Throws vs. Poison have their Strength, Dexterity and Constitution halved. Additionally, the haze obscures the vision of those standing within it, reducing their vision range and movement rate.

The spell's primary effects last for five rounds for creatures who leave the haze.~

